<font face="Arial">
<center><h1> Situation Metaphor (Contd) </h1>

<h2><u> Situation Space</u> </h2></center>
<h2>
<ul>
<li>The Situation Space is the user interaction space in which s/he may
 have used the mobile computer/device as an embedded tool to achieve
 his/her business objectives.</li>


<li>The main <i>Objective</i> of Situated Space is to describe all the 
identified past user-situations in a meaningful way that could be used to 
provide appropriate system behaviour and functionalities. </li>  


<li> The situation space is reagrded as<i>"n-dimensional"</i>space</li>
</ul> 
  <ul type=circle><li> The location has two dimensions
                  -  latitude and longitude </li> </ul>
  <ul type=circle><li> Time is one-dimensional but has logical attributes
                  -  day, month,year etc.</li></ul>
  <ul type=circle><li> User activities and contextual factors vary from
                     situation to situation
</li> </ul>
    

 
</h2>






